{"title":"保护视力","date":"2019-07-28T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 28, 2019","L":"07/28/2019","MM-DD":"07-28"},"updated":"2024-07-01T17:57:02.542Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1dt411c7Zv/\" target=\"_blank\">来自日本的超强眼部训练放松视频，看完我近视都要好了</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://space.bilibili.com/128600590\" target=\"_blank\">高较瘦Amy</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1bx411M7E4\" target=\"_blank\">熬夜玩手机追剧眼睛要瞎？爆红的眼保健操帮你恢复视力</a><br>\n1.转换焦点<br>\n2.视线上下左右移动<br>\n3.眯眼睛<br>\n4.用目光画正方形<br>\n5.眨眼睛<br>\n6.把双手搓热 望向暗处<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1h4411y73P/\" target=\"_blank\">【 恢复视力法（500度以下） 】我国飞行员视力标准的制定者研究推出的一套护眼操</a><br>\n①看手指前后移动3次；②向上下各看3次；③向左、右、上、下各看3次；④眯眼睛3次；⑤顺时针、逆时针各3圈。</p>\n","link":"fit/eyes","comments":true,"plink":"https://vincenteliang.com/fit/eyes/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://vincenteliang.com/fit/eyes/\" title=\"保护视力\">https://vincenteliang.com/fit/eyes/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"July 28, 2019","updated":"July 1, 2024"}}